Package: verisonic-broadcaster
Version: 1.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: VeriSonic <contact@verisonic.com>
Depends: libportaudio2, libasound2t64 | libasound2, libxkbcommon-x11-0, libegl1, wireplumber, pipewire-bin, pipewire-pulse | pulseaudio
Recommends: pulseaudio-utils
Description: VeriSonic Live Broadcaster
 Desktop client for capturing live audio from microphones, line-in, USB interfaces,
 and loopback input devices, then streaming to your VeriSonic radio station.
 Runs as a background tray application with login auto-start.
